                 who="http://papyri.info/editor/users/simoeis">Vote - Accept-Straight-to-Finalization - Line 6: this is a good reading. Cf. the split tau in Sebastou, l. 15.  Verso l. 2: εἰς also looks good. Line 9: I see no reason for the regularization and would keep as is.  See Gonis's remark about the wrong page reference to Olsson.</change>
